<template lang="html">
  <v-form  @submit.prevent="onSubmit">
    <v-container>
      <v-row>
        <v-col
        :cols="6">
          <v-select
              v-if="!editGroupName"
              :items="riskProfileGroups"
              item-text="name"
              item-value="id"
              v-model="shownRP"
              outlined dense hide-details>
          </v-select>
          <v-text-field
            v-else
            :value="shownRPObject.name"
            @change="newGroupName = $event"
            dense outlined
            hide-details />
        </v-col>
        <v-col
        :cols="1">
          <template v-if="canEdit">
            <v-btn
              v-if="!editGroupName"
              color="green" icon
              @click="editGroupName = !editGroupName">
              <v-icon large>mdi-pencil-circle</v-icon>
            </v-btn>
            <v-btn
              v-else
              color="green" icon
              @click="updateGroupName()">
              <v-icon large>mdi-check-circle</v-icon>
            </v-btn>
          </template>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
        :cols="2">
          <v-btn
            color="primary"
            @click="setActiveRP()">
            Set As Active
          </v-btn>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
        :cols="2">
          <AddRPGroup
            :userID="user.id"
            @add-rpgroup="addRPGroup"/>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
        :cols="1">
          <DeleteObj
            v-if="canEdit"
            :objectType="'riskprofilegroup'"
            :objectToDelete="shownRPObject"
            @delete-object="deleteRPGroup($event)"
          />
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row dense>
        <v-col
          :cols="2">

        </v-col>
        <v-col
          v-for="AAName in nameSet"
          :key="Object.keys(AAName)[0]">
          <v-card dense>
            <v-card-text>
              {{ Object.values(AAName)[0] }}
            </v-card-text>
          </v-card>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
          :cols="1"
          align-self="center">
          <AANameConfig
            v-if="canEdit"
            :RPAANames="RPAANames"/>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row
        v-for="profile in riskProfiles"
        :key="profile.id"
        dense>
        <v-col
          :cols="2">
            <v-text-field
              :background-color="checkColor(profile)"
              @change="addToChanged(profile)"
              v-model="profile.name"
              dense outlined
              :hint="checkHint(profile)"
              persistent-hint
              hide-details="auto" />
        </v-col>
        <v-col
          v-for="AAName in nameSet"
          :key="Object.keys(AAName)[0]">
            <v-text-field
              @change="addToChanged(profile)"
              :value = "getAAPercentage(AAName,profile)"
              @blur = "setAAPercentage($event.target.value, AAName, profile)"
              type="number"
              outlined dense hide-details/>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
          :cols="1">
          <DeleteObj
            v-if="canEdit"
            :objectType="'riskprofile'"
            :objectToDelete="profile"
            :shownRP="shownRP"
            @delete-object="getRiskProfiles"
            v-on="$listeners"
          />
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row v-if="canEdit"
        dense>
        <v-col
          :cols="2">
            <v-text-field
              v-model="newRP.name"
              outlined dense hide-details/>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
          v-for="AAName in nameSet"
          :key="Object.keys(AAName)[0]">
            <v-text-field
              type="number"
              v-model="newRP.allocations[Object.keys(AAName)[0]]"
              outlined dense hide-details/>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
          :cols="1">
          <v-btn type="button" color="green" dark dense
            @click="addRP">
            <v-icon>
              mdi-plus
            </v-icon>
          </v-btn>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row v-if="riskProfiles.length && canEdit">
        <v-col :cols="2">
          <v-btn type="submit" color="primary" dark dense>Update All</v-btn>
        </v-col>
        <v-col :cols="2">

        </v-col>
      </v-row>
    </v-container>
  </v-form>
</template>

<script>
import { apiService } from "@/common/api.service.js";
import AANameConfig from "@/components/AANameConfig.vue";
import DeleteObj from "@/components/DeleteObj.vue";
import AddRPGroup from "@/components/AddRPGroup.vue";

export default {
  name: "RiskProfileTable",
  props: {
    riskProfileGroups: {
      type: Array,
      required: true,
    },
    user: {
      type: Object,
      required: false,
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {
      newGroupName: "",
      editGroupName: false,
      riskProfiles: [],
      RPAANames: [],
      error: null,
      shownRP: null,
      changeList: [],
      newRP: {
        name:"",
        order:null,
        allocations:{},
      },
    };
  },
  components: {
    AANameConfig,
    DeleteObj,
    AddRPGroup,

  },
  computed: {
    canEdit() {
      if (this.isPracticeAdmin && this.isNotAFSLLimited ) {
        return true
      } else {
        return false
      }
    },
    isPracticeAdmin() {
      if (this.riskProfileGroups && this.shownRP && this.shownRPObject.id) {
        if (this.shownRPObject.active_practices.length > 0) {
          return this.shownRPObject.active_practices.some(item => this.user.admin_practices.includes(item));
        } else {
          return true
        }
      } else {
        return true
      }
    },
    isNotAFSLLimited() {
      if (this.riskProfileGroups && this.shownRP) {
        if (this.shownRPObject.AFSL_limitation) {
          const i = this.riskProfileGroups.findIndex(item => item.id == this.shownRP);
          return this.riskProfileGroups[i].AFSL_limitation.length < 1
        } else {
          return false
        }
      } else {
        return false
      }
    },
    shownRPObject() {
      if (this.riskProfileGroups && this.shownRP) {
          const i = this.riskProfileGroups.findIndex(item => item.id == this.shownRP);
          if (i != -1) {
            //The id is added to the array before the group data comes back from
            // Profile view, so this avoids errors while it comes in.
            return this.riskProfileGroups[i];
          } else {
            return {}
          }
      } else {
        return {}
      }
    },
    nameSet: function (){
      let AANameList = [];
      let checkList = []
      for (let i = 0; i < this.RPAANames.length; i++) {
        let found = false;
        let aaName = this.RPAANames[i];
          if (checkList.includes(aaName.custom_name)) {
            found = true;
          }
          if (!found) {
            let newAA = {};
            newAA[aaName.id] = aaName.custom_name;
            AANameList.push(newAA);
            found = false;
            checkList.push(aaName.custom_name);
          }
      }
      return (AANameList)
    }
  },
  watch: {
    // user.active_rp: function () {
    //   this.shownRP = this.user.active_rp;
    //   this.getRPAANameData();
    //   this.getRiskProfiles();
    // },
    shownRP: function () {
      this.getRPAANameData();
      this.getRiskProfiles();
    },
  },
  methods: {
    checkHint(profile) {
      if (!this.checkComplete(profile)) {
        return "Allocations do not equal 100%"
      }
    },
    checkColor(profile){
      if (!this.checkComplete(profile)) {
        return "red lighten-4"
      }
    },
    checkComplete(profile) {
      let value = profile.allocations.reduce( function (a,b) {
        return a + Number(b.percentage);
      }, 0);
      if (value == 1) {
        return true
      } else {
        return false
      }
    },
    updateGroupName(){
      this.editGroupName = !this.editGroupName;
      if (this.newGroupName != '') {
        let endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRPObject.id}/`;
        apiService(endpoint, "PATCH", {
          name: this.newGroupName,
        }).then(data => {
          this.$emit('update-rpgroup', data);
          this.newGroupName = "";
        })
      }
    },
    deleteRPGroup(data) {
      this.$emit('delete-rpgroup', data)
      this.riskProfiles = [];
    },
    setActiveRP() {
      let endpoint = `/api/user/${this.user.id}/`;
      apiService(endpoint, "PATCH", {
        active_rp: this.shownRP,
      }).then(data => {
        this.$emit('update-user',data);
      });
    },
    addRPGroup(data){
      this.$emit('add-rpgroup')
      this.shownRP = data.id;
    },
    addToChanged(profile) {
      if (!(this.changeList.includes(profile))) {
        this.changeList.push(profile);
      } else {
        const i = this.changeList.findIndex(item => item.id === profile.id);
        this.changeList.splice(i, 1);
        this.changeList.push(profile);
      }
    },
    setAAPercentage(event, AAName, riskProfile) {
      const i = this.riskProfiles.findIndex(item => item.id === riskProfile.id);
      const aaID = Object.keys(AAName)[0];
      let found = false;
      for (let x=0; x < this.riskProfiles[i].allocations.length; x++){
        found = false;
          if (this.riskProfiles[i].allocations[x].name.id == aaID) {
            // event = event.split("%").pop();
            this.riskProfiles[i].allocations[x].percentage = event/100;
            found = true;
            break;
          }
      }
      if (!found) {
        let newAllocation = {}
        newAllocation.name = {}
        newAllocation.name.id = aaID;
        newAllocation.percentage = event/100;
        newAllocation.riskprofile = riskProfile.id;
        newAllocation.id = null;
        this.riskProfiles[i].allocations.push(newAllocation);
      }
    },
    getAAPercentage(AAName, riskProfile) {
      let percentage = 0
      for (let i=0; i < riskProfile.allocations.length; i++) {
        if (riskProfile.allocations[i].name.custom_name == Object.values(AAName)[0]) {
          percentage += riskProfile.allocations[i].percentage;
        }
      }
      return (percentage*100).toFixed(2)
    },
    getRiskProfiles() {
      if (this.shownRP) {
        let endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRP}/riskprofiles/`;
        apiService(endpoint).then(data => {
          this.riskProfiles = data.results;
        });
      }
    },
    getRPAANameData() {
      if (this.shownRP) {
        let endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRP}/riskprofilenames/`;
        apiService(endpoint).then(data => {
          this.RPAANames = data.results;
        });
      }
    },
    addRP() {
      if (this.newRP.name) {
        let endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRP}/riskprofiles/`;
        apiService(endpoint, "POST", {
          name: this.newRP.name,
          group: this.shownRP,
          order: this.newRP.order,
        }).then(data => {
          this.addAA(data.id);
        });
        if (this.error) {
          this.error = null;
        }
      } else {
        this.error = "You must enter a name for the new risk profile.";
      }
    },
    addAA(id) {
      for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(this.newRP.allocations)) {
        let endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRP}/riskprofiles/${id}/aa/`;
        apiService(endpoint, "POST", {
          name_id: key,
          percentage: value/100,
          riskprofile: id
        }).then(data => {
          this.getRiskProfiles();
          this.newRP.name="";
          this.newRP.order=null;
          this.newRP.allocations = {};
          this.$emit("disable-dialog", data);
        });
      }
    },
    onSubmit() {
      if (this.changeList) {
        for (let i=0; i < this.changeList.length; i++) {
          let endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRP}/riskprofiles/${this.changeList[i].id}/`;
          apiService(endpoint, "PATCH", {
            name: this.changeList[i].name,
            group: this.changeList[i].group,
            order: this.changeList[i].order,
          }).then(data => {
            this.updateAA(data.id, this.changeList[i]);
          });
        };
      };
    },
    updateAA(profileID, profile) {
      for (let i=0; i < profile.allocations.length; i++) {
        let endpoint = '';
        let method = '';
        if (profile.allocations[i].id == null) {
          endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRP}/riskprofiles/${profileID}/aa/`;
          method = "POST"
        } else {
          endpoint = `/api/riskprofilegroups/${this.shownRP}/riskprofiles/${profileID}/aa/${profile.allocations[i].id}/`;
          method = "PATCH"
        };
        apiService(endpoint, method, {
          id: profile.allocations[i].id,
          name_id: profile.allocations[i].name.id,
          percentage: profile.allocations[i].percentage,
          riskprofile: profileID
        }).then(data => {
          this.getRiskProfiles();
          this.$emit("disable-dialog", data);
          this.changeList=[];
        });
      };
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    this.shownRP = this.user.active_rp;
    this.getRPAANameData();
    this.getRiskProfiles();
  }
};
</script>
